<subSubSection id="88DE6550FFB4FFDB0F9CBDB3C348FCEE" pageId="22" pageNumber="296" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="C07B36DBFFB4FFDB0F9CBDB3C348FCEE" blockId="22.[160,1155,674,837]" pageId="22" pageNumber="296">
<emphasis id="F2B0EAC9FFB4FFDB0F9CBDB3C3EDFD11" bold="true" box="[160,424,674,698]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="296">Differential diagnosis.</emphasis>
Lateral margins of pronotum subparallel-sided, posterior corners acute; elytron subparallel-sided. Dorsal colour pattern: pronotum light-yellow, contour and a central stripe on the pronotal disc dark-brown, sometimes with pair of pink vittae. Elytra darkbrown, outer margins light-yellow, except for the dark-brown outline. Flash pattern is unknown.
</paragraph>
